# Lean the ON-BOX docker build context (DSO-100). Build context is the repo root
# (see infra/deploy/compose/*/compose.yml); the image builds need source + the
# pnpm lockfile only. Everything reproducible, heavy, or secret is excluded so the
# context tar stays small and no secret/tfstate is ever shipped into a layer.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
.git
.github
.claude
docs
**/*.md

# Never ship deploy state / secrets into a build layer.
infra/deploy/.env
infra/deploy/terraform/.terraform
infra/deploy/terraform/*.tfstate*
infra/deploy/terraform/*.tfvars
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
!**/.env.example
